Obtaining the data files:

1) Main data:
   - Go to http://tanzil.net/download/
   - Select Uthmani, check everything and XML as the format. Save as quran-uthmani.xml
   - Select Simple Enhanced, check everything and XML as the format. Save as quran-simple-enhanced.xml

2) Metadata:
   - Get quran-data.xml from http://tanzil.net/wiki/Quran_Metadata and save it here

Building:
  qmake && make
  That should generate metadata.h

Logo:
  Original logo from http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bismillah_gold.svg
  Modified by me to get a greenish background ;-)

